 mounted behind the car radiator grill and connected to the incar monitorat opticsplanet we are proud of our great line of flir pathfindir products and we back it by offering free shipping on orders over  we also make shopping easy by having product experts standing by to answer any questions you may have and offering great howto guides and blog posts for information at your fingertips drive with more confidence with the flir pathfindir series  products in flir systems pathfindir filters  categories options deals rating   up    up    up    up  reset price reset or enter your custom price range from  — to  certified by the manufacturer as made in the usa reset reset reset reset show       sort by most popular  most popular price low to high price high to low savings  off avg rating high to low most reviewed first a to z z to a newest first  models flir systems pathfindir ii hz ntsc kit  you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another one to your comparison view compare compare   models flir systems pathfindir ii installation kit as low as  you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another one to your comparison view compare compare  flir systems pathfindir ii ecu mounting bracket  you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another one to your comparison view compare compare   models flir systems gonight pathifndir kit as low as  you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another one to your comparison view compare compare  flir systems pathfinder ir ii pdad fast video kit  you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another one to your comparison view compare compare  flir systems pathfinder ir ii fast video kit  you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another one to your comparison view compare compare  show       reset flir systems pathfindir comments all pathfindir   ca