g situations to narrow your search for just the right equipment from flir use the handy category and product line filters below on the left read through reviews of flir products written by people like you remember a flir warranty ensures your satisfaction with your purchase for more help choosing durable reliable flir products check our informative blogs and our article about the differences between thermal imaging and night vision optics planet proudly supplies needed equipment to military and law enforcement personnel we offer free shipping on all orders over  as well as free shipping to apos and fpos please refer to our apofpo shipping and export restrictions for more information on export to apofpo addresses make opticsplanetcom your trusted procurement source for flir and all other military gear featured flir products  models flir scout ts thermal night vision camera unit as low as  you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another one to your comparison view compare compare  flir systems thermal night vision riflescope x  add to cart for yourspecial price you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another one to your comparison view compare compare  flir systems scout ii  thermal night vision monocular s  free  day shipping you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another one to your comparison view compare compare  flir systems scout tk mini thermal monocular s  free  day shipping you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another one to your comparison view compare compare  flir systems scout iii  thermal night vision monocular   free  day shipping you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another one to your comparison view compare compare  flir systems scout iii  thermal night vision monocular   free  day shipping you can only compare up to  products please remove a product before adding another