berger brent december   flir systems buys securitysystem supplier for  million the oregonian retrieved december     hunsberger brent may   wilsonvillebased flir systems outbids garmin for bankrupt marine gps maker the oregonian retrieved may     flir systems completes acquisition of lorex technology for  million nasdaqflir investorsflircom retrieved    flir systems acquires dvtel inc for  million nasdaqflir investorsflircom retrieved    glaser april  the company behind these pocketsized military surveillance drones just got bought for  million recode retrieved    company overview flir systems inc retrieved  april    information about flir thermal imagers retrieved    a b c d e f g flir systems misses on earnings beats on revs wwwzachscom  april  retrieved  june    a b c  investor presentation pdf flir systems inc retrieved  april   external linksedit goinfraredcom – flir infrared cameras and thermal imagers business data for flir systems google finance yahoo finance reuters sec filings forbes flir systems v t e oregonbased companies nyse listed greenbrier companies lithia motors nike nw natural portland general electric nasdaq listed columbia sportswear electro scientific industries flir lattice radisys schnitzer steel umpqua holdings private companies adec consumer cellular erickson inc esco fei franz bakery hoffman construction infocus kindercare education laika leupold  stevens les schwab the old spaghetti factory parr lumber plaid pantry rentrak resers fine foods roseburg forest products sharis vigor industrial other bimart tillamook creamery western family foods list of companies based in oregon retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleflirsystemsoldid categories companies based in wilsonville oregoncompanies listed on nasdaqelectronics companies established in avionics companies establishments in oregonvideo surveillance companieshidden categories pages using deprecated image syntaxcoordinates not on wikidata navigation menu personal tools not logged in