ooking and engaged and i am empowered to make a difference every day sarah h about us you can make a difference since our founding in  flir has grown substantially today we are the global leader in the design manufacture and marketing of sensor systems created for users in the commercial and government sectors internationally and domestically flir improves the world with innovative infrared sensing and detection technologies designed to keep the planet safe communities healthy and economies productive with an unwavering vision and solid determination this is a fastpaced rapidly changing and dynamic business our people set us apart as the marketleader flir is a busy dynamic place we offer challenging careers and real professional growth in a culture that encourages constant creativity continuous learning and individual responsibility when you join our team you will relish the opportunity to be part of our success because just as our products make a difference to the world everyone who works with us is given the ability to make an impact on our future thanks to the talent and imagination of our people we are the best at what we do working to the highest ethical standards we support the countries and communities in which we trade in addition to our corporate charitable giving program every one of our sites supports local charities and contributes to disaster relief efforts  another way for you to make a difference flir systems find a job opening near you find locations culture how we work our people have established flir as the market leader in the infrared industry so we have built an environment of creativity continuous learning and professional freedom – ideal for flourishing careers creative people from all backgrounds and diverse perspectives give us our energy they bring us new ideas meet challenges and realize their potential the trust of customers shareholders and communities is at the core of our vision and every member of the flir team has the opportunity to make a real contribution to our success our belief in the highest ethical standards is unwavering striving to make a difference we support the countries and communities in which we trade backing local charities and playing our part in disaster relief flir leads the infrared systems market because we are the best at what we do  and that’s no accident it’s thanks to the imagination endeavor and application of the people with whom we work so we believe it is essential that we reward our colleagues properly and show their professional growth health and wellbeing are as important to us as their financial security diversity we celebrate difference we believe diversity gives us a competitive edge in the global marketplace reflecting the different aspects of our customers markets and colleagues it also enables us to be a representative member of the communities in which we live and operate we are dedicated to a culture which values and respects all people and encourages their ideas so diversity is an integral part of the way we do business our success as a global leader depends on it flir systems is an equal opportunity employer as a federal contractor flir is required to participate in the everify program to confirm eligibility to work in the united states for information regarding your legal rights and protections please click here flir is committed to working with and providing reasonable accommodation to individuals with physical and mental disabilities if you need special assistance or an accommodation while seeking employment please email abilitiesflircom we will make a determination on your request for reasonable accommodation on a casebycase basis search jobs its so rewarding to take a product from invention to commercial sale jeremy w benefits how we take care of you at flir our people are the source of our energy our team members have established flir as the market leader in the infrared industry which is why we reward them well and have built an environment of creativity continuous learning and professional freedom – ideal for flourishing careers as a member of the flir team you will always have the opportunity to make a substantial contribution to this principle because we recognize everyone has the ability to drive our future achievements we offer competitive performancebased packages which include base salary the chance to earn cash bonuses and in some cases participation in our longterm incentive program all our teams enjoy generous benefits as we believe it is important to provide a comprehensive rewards system to support your professional growth wellbeing and financial future us benefits our benefit plans are designed to keep our people healthy happy and moving ahead flir benefits are generous and personalized from our fitness subsidy to comprehensive health and vision care programs we let you select the options that are right for you maybe you need braces are planning to adopt a child or have a need for family counselling  whatever your situation we have you covered some benefits may depend on the place you live but we keep the choices as equitable as possible investment benefits flir provides many options to help you establish a financially secure future these include a rich k plan that allows you to defer up to  of your pretax salary we supplement your retirement savings by making a discretionary matching contribution of  cents on every dollar up to the irs allowable annual maximum while our discretionary matching contributions may change from year to year our commitment to helping you save for a secure retirement future won’t you can choose from our traditional pretax k plan or the roth k plan where your contributions are made on an aftertax basis we also offer you an employee stock purchase plan allowing you to contribute up to  of your salary to buy flir stock at a  discount many of our locations also offer credit union membership that includes a checking account bank cards and competitive interest rates health benefits through flir youll have a selection of medical plans for you and your family which includes coverage for domestic partners these plans include a health savings plan and two levels of ppos with several tiers of coverage in addition just in case you can’t get to your doctor when you need to we offer telemedicine through mdlive where you can videoconference or talk by phone with a physician  we also offer generous vision benefits and our dental insurance program provides comprehensive coverage including orthodontia for adults and children income protectionenhancement benefits we offer many benefits to protect you and your family and give you the opportunity to save money many of these are provided without cost to you including a life insurance benefit equal to twice your base salary shortterm and longterm disability coverage and health and dependent care flexible spending accounts we also offer a unique spouse disability program that provides cash benefits if your spouse becomes disabled additional voluntary life and add insurance is also available for you your spouse or domestic partner and eligible children just to make sure you are fully covered we also offer voluntary accident insurance and critical illness insurance family and parenting benefits as well as short term disability and all federal and state family medical leave policies each new parent receives two paid “baby days” we also provide assistance for the costs associated with adoption time off benefits time away from work to be with your family and friends is important as a new team member you will enjoy four weeks of personal time off pto per year one additional day is then added for each year of service over five years your maximum annual pto will be  days flir also observes  holidays each calendar year flir extras our education assistance program reimburses your tuition fees for approved workrelated programs of study some flir facilities have onsite fitness centers and wellness programs we also offer a fitness subsidy that will help you pay for exercise and wellness programs our team members have access to an employee assistance program that provides confidential counselling and other personal services  we encourage our employees to refer amazing candidates to flir through our employee referral program and reward them with referral bonuses community and charitable involvement is an important part of our culture our giving program provides a matching gift of up to  per employee per year to a charity of your choice this is in addition to our many sitesponsored outreach and charitable activities search jobs flir cares about its employees ron n what our employees say sarah h product manager optical gas imaging read testimonial chuck c program manager read testimonial petrina b global program compliance manager read testimonial chris b us national sales director rdscience solutions read testimonial jason m area sales manager distribution uk read testimonial joakim f fpga architect and tech lead read testimonial grégoire o general manager flir maritime read testimonial jeff p phd rd physicist and radiation safety officer read testimonial jeremy w manager science  technology read testimonial ron n product support manager raymarine read testimonial vatche a marketing media specialist read testimonial search jobs my work is never less than varied and interesting jason m our locations search jobs my job has taken me to some amazing places vatche a be visionary at flir we have a simple but ambitious mission to develop marketleading infrared and sensing technologies which enhance everyday life from saving energy to saving lives flir systems is making a real difference in our world our products are used in a wide array of situations to rescue people in danger detect criminals conserve energy navigate safely provide security around the globe and protect our environment search jobs every team is dynamic forwardlooking and engaged and i am empowered to make a difference 