ore quickly and have confidence you didn’t miss something vital model griffin   multimodal sampling gcms the griffin  mobile gas chromatograph mass spectrometer gcms enables innovative multimodal sample introduction to detect and identify complex chemical samples  hours a day  days a week the instrument is able to accept liquid solid and vapor samples as well as provide continuous direct air monitoring the griffin  is the only mobile gcms to provide this range of sample introduction in a single system that also enables msms analysis model e e e and e  flir infrared cameras introducing the flir e e e and e infrared cameras with msxnow you can afford the ultimate inspection tool gain the competitive advantage and take care of more customers blow them away with dramatic msx thermal images that clearly reveal problems from sources of energy loss moisture intrusion and structural issues to overheating electrical and mechanical equipment flir systems  model ptseries  flir multisensor thermal security cameras networkready pantilt multisensor thermal security cameras ptseries thermal security cameras let you see intruders and other threats to your facility’s security clearly in total darkness and in bad weather the ptseries precision pantilt mechanism gives operators accurate pointing control while providing fully programmable scan patterns radar slewtocue and slewtoalarm functionalityfully enabled for control and operation over digital flir systems  model dseries  flir outdoor dome enclosure systems the dseries outdoor dome enclosure provides precision pantilt control while providing fully programmable scan patterns radar slewtocue and slewtoalarm functionality fully enabled for control and operation over ip and serial networks dseries systems deploy a  x  or  ×  pixel thermal imager along with a daynight × zoom color ccd camera flir’s dseries thermal multisensor security dome cameras are the perfect biological detection model fcseries t  flir thermal imaging cameras for traffic monitoring flir thermal imaging cameras are commonly integrated in traffic video detection and monitoring solutions needing no light at all to produce an image they can be used for a wide vatiety of traffic application bioaerosol threats monitor the ibac is a continuouslyoperating monitor that provides early warning of biological aerosol threats the ibac facilitates the process of identifying bioterror agents to allow timely containment treatment and remediation monitors are designed to detect concentrated levels of biological aerosols possible agents released in a biothreat attack can include bacterial spores such as b anthracis which causes anthrax bacteria such as y pestis model c  modular tactical collector the c modular tactical collector is intended to be used as a standalone collector or as a component within a modularlyintegrated system that would also include detection and identification componentsavailable in two standalone versions the cl and the cx the cl has been optimized for longer battery run time while the cx has been optimized for enhanced collection of small particles such as single spores both versions may be building model eseries  flirmsx advanced thermal imaging camera troubleshoot more efficiently create detailed reports easier and share images and findings faster with flir’s latest eseries thermal imagers featuring a fresh array of imaging communication and productivity tools to help you get more done in a day model sc series  flir high performance thermal imaging cameras high performance thermal imaging cameras for industrial educational  thermographythe flir sc series provides a high spatial resolution allowing a highest sensitivity  accuracy its  x  or  x  pixels format indium antimonide insb focal plane array delivers respectively an outstanding  or  hz frame rate while keeping extraordinary linearity and sensitivity figures the use of our latest read out integrated circuit model tseries  flir thermal imaging cameras you need troubleshooting tools that can help you find and report equipment problems fast that’s exactly what tseries cameras do they let you see invisible heat caused by electrical resistance and mechanical wear early enough to help you head off expensive downtime and potential dangerwatch the video to learn why no other line of infrared cameras makes it easier to capture images share findings and get more done with time to spare and be model ax  flir automated multispectral temperature sensor combining thermal and visual cameras in a small affordable package the ax provides continuous temperature monitoring and alarming for uninterrupted condition monitoring of critical electrical and mechanical equipment the ax provides early detection of temperaturerelated issues in electrical and mechanical equipment making it the ideal temperature sensor for continuous condition monitoring and hot spot detection for electrical cabinets process optical gas imaging rediation flir systems one  flir personal thermal imager bring playtime to a whole new level this summer have longer days as you observe wildlife and navigate trails in complete darkness have more restful nights by checking your campsite for animals or a smoldering fire from the comfort of your tent and have more fun putting a spin on a night game of hideandgoseekwhatever your activity of choice you’ll find flir one to be a complete gamechanger flir systems  model gf  refrigerant leak detection infrared cameras the flir gf detects refrigerant gas leaks without interrupting or shutting down operations in food production storage and retail pharmaceutical automotive and air conditioning detecting refrigerant gas leaks early can save on costly replenishment and limit environmental impactrefrigerant gases are highly toxic environmentally harmful and heavily regulated leaks gone unchecked are problematic on many levels from the safety of employees to radiation detection  nanoraider when radiation detection capabilities are necessary oper