reventative maintenance solution to spot leaks in piping flanges and connections in petrochemical operations the infrared camera can rapidly scan large areas and pinpoint leaks in real time it is ideal for monitoring plants that are difficult to reach with contact measurement tools brite star  combat proven laser designation systems the most powerful multisensor targeting system in its class the brite star ii and brite star dp systems are the latest generation of the combatproven brite star laser designation system with a  duty cycle diodepumped laser rangefinderdesignator and inflight boresighting the brite star ii and brite star dp are always ready for action its range performance sensor combination and program record make it the lowrisk choice for reliable star safire family  model ii  gyrostabilized eoir systems multimission awr certified imaging solution for hh and uh blackhawk variants the world standard in x insb thermal imaging star safire ii can carry up to five separate payloads longrange thermal imager lowlight tv ultra longrange spotter scope laser rangefinder and laser illuminator fully awrcertified for use on us army uh  hh a and l model blackhawks the star safire ii is combatproven reliable and ready model iii  gyrostabilized eoir systems the multimission imaging solution for land and air applications the star safire iii is one of the world’s most popular gyrostabilized eoir systems carrying seven payloads and testedqualified beyond mil specs this system is the workhorse for airborne land and maritime force protection and medevac in hotspots around the world over  star safire iii’s have been delivered to the us military nato and nations worldwide markir  infrared emitters the markir tuned band emitters utilize a twodimensional photonic crystal structure to tune and restrict the ir emission for visibility in only the desired spectral region these miniature devices provide high energy infrared signals with minimal power consumption thus enabling longran