llow the operator to see in total darkness adverse weather and through such air pollutants as smoke and haze toward the end of the s flir began to leverage its experience in infrared imaging technology to develop handheld and laboratory systems for a variety of commercial applications that required not only superior image quality but also the ability to detect and measure temperature differences this effort accelerated with the acquisition of the industrial infrared imaging group from the hughes aircraft co in  the acquisition of agema sweden in  and of inframetrics boston ma in mid provided flir engineering teams and sales and support infrastructure that accelerated flir’s success in commercial thermal imaging markets together agema and inframetrics represented over  years of significant infrared camera development and thermography applications expertise agema developed the first commercial infrared scanner designed for powerline inspections in  the first batteryoperated portable infrared scanner in  the first dualwavelength system capable of realtime analog recording for rd markets in  and the first uncooled infrared camera the agema  and  inframetrics also a pioneer in commercial infrared cameras and thermography training developed the first tvcompatible infrared system in  and the first fullfeatured camcorderstyle focal plane array fpa infrared camera in  in  flir acquired indigo systems a leading developer and supplier of a wide range of infrared imaging products including cooled and uncooled infrared detectors camera cores and finished cameras ever since flir has invested in numerous adjacent markets technologies and products to expand its sensor solution set and its ability to service a broader set of customers these investments have enabled significant growth in revenue and unit volumes which has helped reduce the cost and thus end user prices of the products this has resulted in dramatic increases in customers as well as increased global awareness of the power of thermal technology currently flir operates in many locations around the globe and employs a total of over  dedicated employees most popular related searches sf gas detection mobile gas chromatograph mass spectrometer chemical vapor detection chemical vapor detection system infrared gas imaging system gas leak detection optical imaging camera powerline inspection airborne powerline inspection gas leak detection camera chemical vapor analysis featured products model   radiation detection  identifinder flir  model gfx   intrinsically safe ogi camera radiation detection  nanoraider flir systems  model gf  flir furnace and electrical inspections infrared cameras model tg  flir imaging ir thermometer model ax  flir automated multispectral temperature sensor star safire family  model ii  gyrostabilized eoir systems brite star  combat proven laser designation systems flir  model gf   refrigerant leak detection infrared cameras model sc series  flir high performance thermal imaging cameras featured software flir webviewer flir tools software flir videoreport software flir reporter pro featured downloads flir  ax  temperature sensor brochure flir  model gf  refrigerant leak detection infrared cameras  brochure flir  model gf  detection and electrical inspections infrared cameras  brochure flir  model gf  furnace and electrical inspections infrared cameras  brochure flir  model gf  gas leak detection and electrical inspections infrared cameras brochure flir  model dm   trms digital multimeter manual flir  model cm x  clamp meter brochure flir  model gfx   intrinsically safe ogi camera brochure flir  model gf   refrigerant leak detection infrared cameras brochure flir  model gf   detection and electrical inspections infrared cameras brochure contact supplier contact supplier your message your email your first name your last name i would like to receive periodic email updates and special offers from select suppliers yes please match my request to similar suppliers using x