us pro is built with industryleading flir thermalimaging technology when mounted to dad’s gun or used as a handheld spotting scope zeus pro detects minute differences in the temperatures of both live and inert objects and amplifies these differences to project amazingly clear images onto the unit’s screen utilizing flir’s fieldproven tau®  thermal camera core the zeus pro is available in x or x pixel formats with professionalgrade mm or mm germanium ge objective lenses the result is a wide variety of optical magnifications and the ability to detect an averagesized person up to  yards away eight distinct models optimized for both medium and longrange performance are availabledad will definitely appreciate the armasight by flir zeus pro thermal weapon sight’s simple and intuitive controls functions and features zeus pro models mount and dismount quickly and easily via a milstd rail and feature ballistic reticles an electronic compass and an inclinometer for finer range estimation and target orientation an included multipin connector provides videooutvideoin capability external power supply and support of accessories like an optional dvr or modular range finder operation and functions are also supported by an included wireless remotethink dad already has everything think again say thanks this father’s day by presenting him with the unrivaled vision of zeus we can’t predict his reaction but one thing’s for certain even if he does have  kids you just became his favorite again recent posts what do  million bats look like in thermal flir maritime introduces first cooled thermal camera to awardwinning mseries line flir m celebrating  years of innovation a history of aerial observation flir thermal snake feeding flir systems introduces highperformance raymarine axiom pro multifunction displays flir receives “red dot best of the best”  award for flir exxseries categories hot topics product news featured top feature all comments electrical  mechanical   flir tg flir cseries fl