swim using small drones equipped with both thermal and visible cameras allows the ocean alliance researchers to collect comparative data without harming or disturbing the animals in their natural habitatslearn more about the snotbot and how flir is used on the ocean alliance website photos courtesy of ocean alliance recent posts what do  million bats look like in thermal flir maritime introduces first cooled thermal camera to awardwinning mseries line flir m celebrating  years of innovation a history of aerial observation flir thermal snake feeding flir systems introduces highperformance raymarine axiom pro multifunction displays flir receives “red dot best of the best”  award for flir exxseries categories hot topics product news featured top feature all comments electrical  mechanical   flir tg flir cseries flir e e e  e flir e e  e flir e e  e flir t t  t flir tseries flir t t t  t flir tk test  measurement tools ir windows   building   flir cseries flir e e e  e flir ebx ebx  ebx flir e e  e flir tbx tbx tbx  tbx flir tseries flir tk test  measurement tools   test  measurement   flir dm imaging multimeter flir tg spot thermal camera flir tg spot thermal camera flir mr imaging moisture meter flir mr imaging moisture meter flir mr imaging moisture meter flir flexible clamp meters flir dm digital multimeter flir dm digital multimeter flir cm power clamp flir cm power clamp flir cm power clamp flir cm clamp with ir thermometer flir vp voltage detector flir im insulation  dmm combo flir mr moisture meter flir vs videoscope airtec intellirockextech   gas detection systems   flir gfx flir gf flir gf flir gf flir gf flir gf flir gf   automation   flir compact aseries flir a  a flir apt  af flir aex flir a  a flir ax flir a flir gpt flir ga mio   personal vision systems   flir one flir fx flir scout series flir thermosight rseries   research  development   industrial rd academics  research nondestructive testing ndt  materials testing defense  aerospace   marine   flir fi