gh the molecules however many gases have infrared absorption characteristics that can be targeted with specially designed thermal imaging cameras watch this great video on how optical gas imaging cameras work   gain a greater understanding of optical gas imaging technology and how you can use it to find and repair gas leaks quickly by downloading our free professional guide   recent posts what do  million bats look like in thermal flir maritime introduces first cooled thermal camera to awardwinning mseries line flir m celebrating  years of innovation a history of aerial observation flir thermal snake feeding flir systems introduces highperformance raymarine axiom pro multifunction displays flir receives “red dot best of the best”  award for flir exxseries categories hot topics product news featured top feature all comments electrical  mechanical   flir tg flir cseries flir e e e  e flir e e  e flir e e  e flir t t  t flir tseries flir t t t  t flir tk test  measurement tools ir windows   building   flir cseries flir e e e  e flir ebx ebx  ebx flir e e  e flir tbx tbx tbx  tbx flir tseries flir tk test  measurement tools   test  measurement   flir dm imaging multimeter flir tg spot thermal camera flir tg spot thermal camera flir mr imaging moisture meter flir mr imaging moisture meter flir mr imaging moisture meter flir flexible clamp meters flir dm digital multimeter flir dm digital multimeter flir cm power clamp flir cm power clamp flir cm power clamp flir cm clamp with ir thermometer flir vp voltage detector flir im insulation  dmm combo flir mr moisture meter flir vs videoscope airtec intellirockextech   gas detection systems   flir gfx flir gf flir gf flir gf flir gf flir gf flir gf   automation   flir compact aseries flir a  a flir apt  af flir aex flir a  a flir ax flir a flir gpt flir ga mio   personal vision systems   flir one flir fx flir scout series flir thermosight rseries   research  development   industrial rd academics  research nondestructive testing