ies commit to your code  we are excited to welcome four new teams as part of our flir one developer community—beerpongcom for their application to test intoxication levels heat check a human detection app rescuer a search and rescue aid app for first responders as well as our ultimate grand prize winners sunscreen checkr for their application to let you know where you missed a spot when applying sunscreen our winners sunscreen checkr will be traveling to visit flir santa barbara to pitch their app ideas to the flir team thanks again to everyone who made this event possible and a very special thanks to all participants      to learn more about the flir one developer program head to developerflircom recent posts what do  million bats look like in thermal flir maritime introduces first cooled thermal camera to awardwinning mseries line flir m celebrating  years of innovation a history of aerial observation flir thermal snake feeding flir systems introduces highperformance raymarine axiom pro multifunction displays flir receives “red dot best of the best”  award for flir exxseries categories hot topics product news featured top feature all comments electrical  mechanical   flir tg flir cseries flir e e e  e flir e e  e flir e e  e flir t t  t flir tseries flir t t t  t flir tk test  measurement tools ir windows   building   flir cseries flir e e e  e flir ebx ebx  ebx flir e e  e flir tbx tbx tbx  tbx flir tseries flir tk test  measurement tools   test  measurement   flir dm imaging multimeter flir tg spot thermal camera flir tg spot thermal camera flir mr imaging moisture meter flir mr imaging moisture meter flir mr imaging moisture meter flir flexible clamp meters flir dm digital multimeter flir dm digital multimeter flir cm power clamp flir cm power clamp flir cm power clamp flir cm clamp with ir thermometer flir vp voltage detector flir im insulation  dmm combo flir mr moisture meter flir vs videoscope airtec intellirockextech   gas detection systems   flir gfx flir